2.00	I_am_a_fugitive_from_a_chain_gang	I Am a Fugitive from a Chain Gang	I Am a Fugitive from a Chain Gang is a Pre-Code crime/drama film starring Paul Muni as a wrongfully convicted convict on a chain gang who escapes to Chicago. The film was written by Howard J. Green and Brown Holmes from Robert Elliott Burns's autobiography, I Am a Fugitive from a Georgia Chain Gang! that was serialised in True Detective magazine. It was directed by Mervyn LeRoy.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b8/IAmaFugitivefromaChainGang.jpg
